<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span><span class="c4">[الاخرنفاش]</span>،<span class="c5"> بالشين معجمة:</span><a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
